# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:13
translate chinese jamies2_adb78891:

    # pc "Do you have any pets?"
    pc "你有养宠物吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:15
translate chinese jamies2_8a223c68:

    # gnd "Not anymore. I had a dog, Jellybean. Remember her?"
    gnd "现在没有了。我以前养过一只狗，叫杰利豆。还记得她吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:16
translate chinese jamies2_22793db9:

    # pc "Yeah, the little fat chihuahua."
    pc "嗯，那只胖乎乎的小吉娃娃。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:18
translate chinese jamies2_1291be1b:

    # gnd "Right! She was so fat."
    gnd "对！它真的很胖。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:20
translate chinese jamies2_d206d2f4:

    # gnd "Anyway, she died last year."
    gnd "总之，它去年去世了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:21
translate chinese jamies2_5a04c590:

    # gnd "I haven't felt like getting a new dog since then. Not sure I ever will."
    gnd "从那以后我就没想过再养狗。也不确定以后会不会再养。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:23
translate chinese jamies2_af03bdee:

    # gnd "I love dogs, but it's really hard to say goodbye to them, you know?"
    gnd "我喜欢狗，但跟它们告别真的很难，你知道吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:24
translate chinese jamies2_2c3da083:

    # gnd "And no other animals for me. I'm allergic to cats, so that's out."
    gnd "而且我不能养别的动物。我对猫过敏，所以猫不行。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:26
translate chinese jamies2_1043b1ad:

    # gnd "Maybe a turtle one day."
    gnd "也许哪天养只乌龟吧。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:27
translate chinese jamies2_2f0fe011:

    # pc "A turtle?"
    pc "乌龟？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiesurface2.rpy:29
translate chinese jamies2_aa10cc5c:

    # gnd "Yeah, I like turtles. And bonus - they live a long time."
    gnd "是啊，我喜欢乌龟。而且还有个好处——它们寿命很长。"

